Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.32,0:00:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fade(100,100)}{\pos(509,404)\3c&H7F1E2C&}Hamada Masatoshi
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.32,0:00:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fade(100,100)}{\3c&H7F1E2C&\pos(230,404)}Matsumoto Hitoshi
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.79,0:00:10.36,Hamada,,0,0,0,,So, Matsumoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.49,0:00:11.49,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Yes yes yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.36,0:00:11.89,Hamada,,0,0,0,,We’ve done this 3 times in the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.89,0:00:14.26,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Kogal, S&M queen, anime character
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.59,0:00:15.33,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,That is indeed correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.26,0:00:16.13,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Those are the cosplays we’ve done.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.33,0:00:16.86,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,We’ve done a lot of cosplaying.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.13,0:00:17.36,Hamada,,0,0,0,,For the bus tour.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.86,0:00:18.93,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Yep, that’s what we did.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.36,0:00:19.36,Hamada,,0,0,0,,This time, it’s Pink Lady.*
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.36,0:00:22.00,Translator's Note,,0,0,0,,{\pos(361,34)}*Translator’s notes: Pink Lady was a J-Pop duo from the 70s.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.46,0:00:20.70,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Indeed, Pink Lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.70,0:00:22.70,Hamada,,0,0,0,,That’s what the decision came to.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.07,0:00:25.20,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,{\pos(443,336)}Yes, when I heard that we’re going to be doing Pink Lady, I knew I definitely had to be Mie-chan.*
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.07,0:00:30.69,Translator's Note,,0,0,0,,{\pos(365,59)}*Translator’s notes: Real name is Mitsuya Nemoto, but went by the stage name, Mie-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.73,0:00:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(116,337)}Rules:
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.73,0:00:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(355,432)}The games will take place inside the bus. The duo who loses 3 times must be dropped off in the middle of the city and they must sing and dance like Pink Lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.20,0:00:28.34,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,{\fs26}That was the case so... I was graciously given the role of Mie-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.77,0:00:28.24,Hamada,,0,0,0,,{\pos(408,312)}Oh is that so…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.24,0:00:30.21,Hamada,,0,0,0,,{\pos(426,342)}Well, that’s okay with me, I don’t really care.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.71,0:00:33.18,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Let's bring out the participants,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.18,0:00:35.18,Hamada,,0,0,0,,the first duo is the following!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.21,0:00:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yamasaki is partnered up with Director Komurasaki, commonly acknowledged
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.68,0:00:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,as Yamasaki’s most trusted friend at the moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.22,0:00:44.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fade(100,100)\3c&H7F1E2C&\pos(178,340)\fs25}Yamasaki Hosei
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.22,0:00:44.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fade(100,100)\3c&H7F1E2C&\fs25\pos(498,340)}Komurasaki Kozo (Director)
