Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.08,0:00:44.49,Default,,0,0,0,,They’re competing as Pink Lady from their hit, “Wanted"!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.79,0:00:46.89,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,What the hell is this.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.46,0:00:48.06,Hamada,,0,0,0,,This is a duo fight, why the hell are you two together?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.39,0:00:50.39,Yamasaki,,0,0,0,,Well, Komu (Komurasaki)…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.36,0:00:51.90,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Where’s this confidence coming from?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.90,0:00:53.90,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,It’s like you’re saying, “Feel free to praise me.”
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.20,0:00:55.60,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,So creepy…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.60,0:00:57.60,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Thank ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.47,0:00:58.47,Yamasaki,,0,0,0,,Thank ya.
