Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.16,0:04:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(355,400)\c&HD91732&\3c&HFFFFFF&}Cream Stew\N\N\N\N{\c&H170E70&}IN DANGER!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.33,0:04:59.33,Ueda,,0,0,0,,Wait, does that mean for the both of us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.14,0:05:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,From here, the development heats up with the Chihara Brothers continuing into the danger zone right after Cream Stew.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.94,0:05:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And following that, Director Komurasaki messes up, which brings the Yamasaki and Komu duo also in the danger zone!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.08,0:05:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,However, Tanaka makes a mistake and now Cocorico is in the running for the batsu game!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.65,0:05:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,So Downtown is still safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.52,0:05:21.52,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Wait, so everyone is in danger except for us?
