Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.79,0:05:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs24\pos(243,397)}Cream\N Stew:
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.79,0:05:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs24\pos(359,386)}Downtown:
