Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.79,0:05:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs24\pos(585,397)}Yamasaki\N & Komu:
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.96,0:05:22.96,Arita,,0,0,0,,Shit shit shit shit shit
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.22,0:05:24.26,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Okay, starting with Tanaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.26,0:05:25.23,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,Here I go.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.33,0:05:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn’t say it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.40,0:05:34.94,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,No no, I said it all at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.86,0:05:32.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(373,387)\c&HC21F1D&\3c&HFFFFFF&}Downtown: \N\N\NMatsumoto is {\c&H55CCF1&\3c&H000000&}OUT
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.87,0:05:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(355,400)\c&HD91732&\3c&HFFFFFF&}Downtown\N\N\N\N{\c&H170E70&}IN DANGER!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.94,0:05:39.04,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,I said, “UFO! ...You know.” I even added “you know”!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.04,0:05:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,All in. Going all in.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.44,0:05:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fade(100,100)}{\c&HF77A62&\pos(362,317)}Everyone in danger!
