Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.52,0:10:26.85,Endo,,0,0,0,,Starting with Junior!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.92,0:10:31.92,Endo,,0,0,0,,No, not me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.69,0:10:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.29,0:10:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(377,270)}Pointed at Endo who is already out.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.29,0:10:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(373,387)\c&HC21F1D&\3c&HFFFFFF&}Downtown: \N\N\NHamada is {\c&H55CCF1&\3c&H000000&}OUT
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.09,0:10:41.87,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,I can’t even laugh, he’s senile. Senile in his forties.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.87,0:10:43.87,Endo,,0,0,0,,Then we shouldn’t be laughing.
