Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.37,0:10:46.07,Endo,,0,0,0,,Hamada, please start.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.44,0:10:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.91,0:10:53.91,Arita,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.04,0:10:54.04,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,Before that…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.18,0:10:56.55,Arita,,0,0,0,,How about this guy!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.55,0:10:57.55,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.30,0:11:00.21,Ueda,,0,0,0,,He didn’t say “Gets”!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.21,0:11:00.21,Arita,,0,0,0,,He didn’t say it! He didn’t say it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.61,0:11:00.61,Hamada,,0,0,0,,You didn’t say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.58,0:11:04.42,Hamada,,0,0,0,,{\pos(355,400)\c&HD91732&\3c&HFFFFFF&}Downtown\N\N\N\N{\c&H170E70&}IN DANGER!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.62,0:11:03.72,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,The hell, why are YOU saying I didn’t say it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.95,0:11:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn’t though.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.62,0:11:11.16,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,No, no, I thought, “What’s the point in me saying it?”
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.26,0:11:13.73,Endo,,0,0,0,,Out!!
