Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.21,0:11:29.28,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Wait, what? Did he point at him?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.64,0:11:32.64,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,You just had this dull look on your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.35,0:11:35.95,Endo,,0,0,0,,Downtown
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.95,0:11:44.16,Endo,,0,0,0,,You’ll be dropped off in the middle of Roppongi in front of Don Quijote where there are plenty of people there to go shopping.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.53,0:11:48.33,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Hold on, I still can’t get over his mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.33,0:11:54.57,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,He points at Endo, then he does absolutely nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.57,0:11:57.97,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,He’s just there as if he didn’t do anything wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.34,0:12:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fade(100,100)\pos(163,49)}Roppongi Intersection
