Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.76,0:23:16.06,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Really though, Ueda, something’s wrong with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.06,0:23:17.93,Ueda,,0,0,0,,With me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.96,0:23:18.96,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.93,0:23:20.23,Arita,,0,0,0,,He’s the host, the host. It’s fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.23,0:23:24.74,Arita,,0,0,0,,I mean, this show is going to keep continuing and all.
